Section: libs
Architecture: linux-any
Multi-Arch: same
Pre-Depends: ${misc:Pre-Depends}
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Wireless tools - library
 Library used to manipulate the Linux Wireless Extensions, an
